description:
Equip this outfit to cosplay as Sena Kitada, one-half of the idol duo Dirty Bloody Princesses (DBP) from AKIBA'S TRIP: Hellbound & Debriefed.
This DLC will unlock the outfit for purchase in-game.

This DLC includes the following costume items:
DBP Boombox (weapon)
Sena's DBP Blouse (upper wear)
Sena's DBP Pants (lower wear)
Sena's Underwear (underwear)
Sena's DBP Boots (footwear)

*You will need the base game (sold separately) and the latest version of the software to use this DLC.
name: Sena Kitada's Outfit
